subject: Rajasthan History
question_en: Which village played a significant role during the Battle of Haldighati?
question_hi: हल्दीघरत्तम के बारे में महत्ता किस गाँव था?
explanation_en: The village of Kishangarh played a significant role during the Battle of Haldighati. It was the stronghold of Maharana Pratap and his army faced a strong resistance from the army of Akbar led by Mirza Abu Bakr.
